stanford university international undergraduate community welcome to iuc at stanford university the international undergraduate community iuc is the official student group which serves and unites the diverse international undergraduates at stanford it also acts as a support network for internationals here at stanford helping incoming freshmen adjust to a different culture by coordinating with bechtel i center to organize the international new student orientation and other social events for international students iuc events are open to not only international students but also anyone who has studied overseas has international experience or is simply interested in meeting people from around the world stanford university international undergraduate community home photos & website by ahmad anwar all rights reserved 2009
